140 PRINT " PROGRAM TO CALCULATE THE 'TRADITIONAL' FERMI FUNCTIONS FOR "

150 PRINT " BETA (-) AND BETA (+) DECAY. NO CORRECTIONS FOR FINITE NUCLEAR "

160 PRINT " SIZE OR SCREENING BY ORBITAL ELECTRONS ARE MADE. "

170 PRINT

180 PRINT "****************************************************************"

